message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the sub-category for Sound and Music Computing, which is the most relevant sub-category for this paper as it deals with modeling sound fields. Other likely sub-categories could include cs.IT (Information Theory) as the paper deals with coherence functions, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as the concept of spatial coherence is relevant in network analysis, cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) as the paper involves modeling and simulation, and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) as the paper deals with modeling a physical phenomenon.
